00:31:24.920 --> 00:31:27.400
We went to a djinn wedding.

00:31:28.640 --> 00:31:31.000
The djinn took Shams!

00:31:31.280 --> 00:31:33.640
Listen, don't waste my time
or the prosecutor's time.

00:31:34.040 --> 00:31:36.520
A woman is missing,
and you're the prime suspect.

00:31:36.960 --> 00:31:39.200
Tell me what happened
between you and Shams in that house.

00:31:39.320 --> 00:31:41.000
I swear to God I'm not lying!

00:31:42.760 --> 00:31:45.320
We went to a jinn wedding.
The djinn took Shams!

00:31:45.440 --> 00:31:46.800
It was a djinn wedding!

00:31:54.720 --> 00:31:57.840
Stay here. I'll check the generator
and come back.

00:32:14.280 --> 00:32:17.760
I swear I won't say anything.
I'll stay quiet.

00:32:18.120 --> 00:32:19.880
I swear I won't talk.

00:32:32.200 --> 00:32:35.120
Once Shams entered the house,
we couldn't get her out.

00:32:54.520 --> 00:32:56.520
I told you, you wouldn't be able
to handle the story.

00:33:04.760 --> 00:33:06.280
Thank you for your time.

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:15.800
I'm sorry to have bothered you.

00:33:17.280 --> 00:33:18.480
Sorry.

00:33:19.400 --> 00:33:20.840
Do you want my advice?

00:33:27.120 --> 00:33:28.400
Forget what I told you.

00:33:30.760 --> 00:33:32.120
And don't tell anyone about it.

00:33:36.160 --> 00:33:37.680
Delete the recording.

00:33:40.320 --> 00:33:41.920
Don't ever listen to it.

00:33:47.920 --> 00:33:49.720
Welcome, how can I help you?

00:33:50.160 --> 00:33:52.000
I'm here about Shams's disappearance.

00:33:52.160 --> 00:33:54.360
The singer Noura is the prime suspect
in the case.

00:33:55.200 --> 00:33:57.520
The case is still open
and has been handed to another unit.

00:33:57.840 --> 00:34:00.120
May I ask why the charges
against Noura didn't stick?

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:02.120
Because we didn't find a body.

00:34:02.760 --> 00:34:05.520
Without a body, we can't determine
the cause of death or the weapon.

00:34:06.200 --> 00:34:08.520
And we can't link a killer to the crime
without a murder weapon.

00:34:08.720 --> 00:34:11.360
- So you think it's murder?
- There's no other explanation.

00:34:11.680 --> 00:34:13.520
If she were alive, we'd
know her whereabouts

00:34:13.680 --> 00:34:15.160
or someone would have seen her.

00:34:15.400 --> 00:34:17.720
And there's no evidence she left Kuwait
through any border crossing.

00:34:19.600 --> 00:34:21.520
What did Noura say
to defend herself?

00:34:22.840 --> 00:34:26.400
Djinn.
She said the djinn took Shams.

00:34:28.240 --> 00:34:30.480
I actually spoke to her.
She told me the same thing.

00:34:31.880 --> 00:34:33.000
But what do you think?

00:34:34.560 --> 00:34:38.120
Our work doesn't rely on the supernatural,
we only rely on evidence.

00:34:41.240 --> 00:34:43.360
But there is something strange
and unnatural about this case.

00:34:44.600 --> 00:34:45.680
Which is?

00:34:56.880 --> 00:34:59.920
I went to the house where Noura
and Shams were before she disappeared

00:35:00.200 --> 00:35:01.640
looking for evidence.

00:35:25.520 --> 00:35:27.600
When I entered, I felt a strange heat.

00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:33.520
The heat inside that house was
unnaturally higher than the outside

00:35:34.120 --> 00:35:36.160
even though the windows
were open and broken.

00:35:37.160 --> 00:35:39.320
There was no explanation
for the rise in temperature.

00:35:51.680 --> 00:35:53.120
And I saw something strange.

00:36:00.360 --> 00:36:03.320
I saw hoofprints,
but the size wasn't normal.

00:36:03.600 --> 00:36:05.640
They were much larger
than they should be.

00:36:36.240 --> 00:36:39.280
And in one of the ground floor rooms,
I found animal bones.

00:36:45.280 --> 00:36:48.760
Some were still fresh,
which means they were recent.

00:36:51.720 --> 00:36:55.320
Marzouqa says bones are food for djinn,
according to the Hadith.

00:36:58.360 --> 00:37:01.960
But I also saw stray dog tracks there,
so maybe the bones were from their hunting.

00:37:22.400 --> 00:37:25.800
On the walls of the second floor
I found writings, talismans

00:37:25.920 --> 00:37:27.600
strange pictures and statues.

00:37:30.400 --> 00:37:32.200
I think some people took advantage
of the house being abandoned...

00:37:32.320 --> 00:37:34.240
and turned it into something
like an art exhibit.

00:38:48.240 --> 00:38:49.920
The house was completely empty.

00:38:52.840 --> 00:38:57.240
Except for a picture I found upstairs
that looked like Shams.

00:38:58.360 --> 00:39:00.600
Or maybe I just imagined
it looked like her, I don't know.

00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:28.000
How do you explain what you saw?

00:39:28.160 --> 00:39:30.320
I told you, we're men of law.
We follow evidence.

00:39:31.040 --> 00:39:33.560
If we open the door to the supernatural,
it will never end.

00:39:34.760 --> 00:39:37.960
A killer could blame his crime on djinn,
a thief could accuse djinn of stealing.

00:39:38.880 --> 00:39:42.200
- The law doesn't rely on that.
- You're right.

00:39:44.640 --> 00:39:46.440
- One last request, if I may.
- Go ahead.

00:39:46.880 --> 00:39:48.560
Can I see the picture
you found in the house?

00:39:50.480 --> 00:39:51.720
I kept a copy.

00:39:52.960 --> 00:39:54.360
"Case number 483-B"

00:40:04.000 --> 00:40:05.120
Here.

00:40:12.640 --> 00:40:14.320
It looks like the description Noura gave.

00:40:46.600 --> 00:40:49.080
Forget what I told you,
and don't listen to the recording.

00:41:04.160 --> 00:41:06.640
"I woke up terrified
from the nightmare I had."

00:41:07.160 --> 00:41:08.840
"I ran to the door."

00:41:09.760 --> 00:41:13.920
"When I stepped into the hallway,
I felt someone watching me from the left."

00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:20.000
"When I turned, it was the same woman
I saw in the nightmare!"

00:41:33.760 --> 00:41:34.840
Who's there?

00:41:42.840 --> 00:41:43.960
Who's there?

00:42:41.320 --> 00:42:46.200
"Journalist Mishal Zayed Shreida
dies under mysterious circumstances."

00:43:00.800 --> 00:43:01.920
Sing!

00:43:05.240 --> 00:43:06.400
Sing!

00:43:06.960 --> 00:43:10.040
"I met a handsome dark‑skinned man"

00:43:11.600 --> 00:43:13.680
"He signaled to me with his eyes"

00:43:14.680 --> 00:43:17.880
"He spoke to me, and I answered"

00:43:18.800 --> 00:43:21.320
"And I followed him"

00:43:22.640 --> 00:43:27.640
"He said 'don't leave me.
Don't disappear'..."